    "updated_at": "2024-07-03T14:31:49Z",
    "body": "Never-mind, this issue appears to be caused by extraneous space between segments.\r\n\r\n```toml\r\nright_format = \"\"\"\r\n$status\r\n$cmd_duration\r\n$jobs\r\n\"\"\"\r\n```\r\n\r\nshould have been\r\n\r\n```toml\r\nright_format = \"\"\"\r\n$status\\\r\n$cmd_duration\\\r\n$jobs\r\n\"\"\"\r\n```\r\n\r\nSorry for the red herring.",
